title: L'Oreal Paris Colour Rays Hair Color, Fuschia Flash
description: Color rays are bright, highly visible highlights that show up on even the darkest hair. In one simple step, you can swirl on a few bold flashes, brighten up bangs, or brush on an all-over effect.

title: Kleancolor Neon Nail Lacquer - Candy Cast - Mini Collection (NPC593)
description: KleanColor presents its long wearing and chip-resistant Nail Lacquers in petite, travel-friendly size. The set features bright neon colors for playfulness to complete the look of sweet girl who enjoys her creativity.

title: OPI Nail Lacquer, Pirates of The Caribbean Collection, Stranger Tides, 0.5 Fluid Ounce
description: The Pirates of the Caribbean collection captures the bright colors and breathtaking adventure of the Disney release. Trend-settings shades of pink, lavender, sage and the new silver shatter.
